Mercer Capital Advisers, Inc. â€” Investment Process






Contact Us | Directions













INVESTMENT PROCESS






 Personalized Approach â€” Investment strategies are geared to suit the various risk tolerances and objectives of each client.


The stock selection process is based on long-term value, not short-term momentum.
  Equity investments are directed into superior businesses that can be purchased
  at reasonable prices.

As a registered investment advisor, Mercer Capital is compensated by a quarterly management fee based on account value, not commission from transactions. We are incentivized to grow your assets, not shuffle them around.

Clients receive a quarterly performance report, portfolio appraisal, and strategy
  overview in addition to regular monthly brokerage statements and purchase/sale
  confirmations.


Communication is encouraged. We like clients to call and ask questions. In-person portfolio reviews are scheduled on a regular basis.











